text:
Yeah, I use JavaScript to pull the email address and populate it on the next slide (where the field is hidden with CSS) when I creates a multi-step form on the same page.

*EDIT: jQuery actually, using .val()

    var userEmail = $('#hs_form_target_form-number-'+currentSlide+' form input[type="email"]').val();
    $('#hs_form_target_form-number-'+nextSlide+' form input[type="email"]').val(userEmail);
